data.description: Welcome to refined living in this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom sanctuary that effortlessly combines modern elegance with everyday practicality. Step inside and be greeted by a spacious open-concept layout, seamlessly connecting the living, dining and kitchen areas. The kitchen, adorned with granite countertops and a large island, stands as the heart of this home—a place where culinary creations and cherished memories intertwine. At the front of the home, a flexible room awaits—a home office, creative studio, or a cozy retreat for your hobbies. Escape to the outdoors that reveal a generously sized, completely fenced-in backyard. Picture serene evenings on the covered patio, enjoying the private retreat that this home offers. Centrally located 5310 Laustin puts you in the heart of convenience, surrounded by a myriad of shopping and dining options. Just 15 minutes down the road is Fort Cavazos, TX. Don’t miss the opportunity to make it yours!
